title: The Chair Company | Episode 6 Preview

author: HBO Max
description:
Jason Fuchs (Co-Showrunner, Executive Producer, Writer) and Brad Caleb Kane (Co-Showrunner, Executive Producer, Writer) join Marc and Princess to unpack #ITWelcomeToDerry Episode Three and the generational horror that shapes Derry’s past and present. They explore how the town itself becomes an accomplice to evil--through memory, forgetting, and the land beneath it--and how those themes connect to Dick Hallorann’s power. 

Then, actor Kimberly Guerrero (Rose) joins the show to discuss her portrayal of Rose and reclaiming Indigenous narratives.
